{"tid":2233890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國3監獄人員涉向囚犯「洗腦式」播《Baby Shark》遭起訴虐待囚犯","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:52:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T13:34:18.000Z","uid":30040,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"352a3e632c6175ed893349fda7fe02ee4c07623a","tid":2233890,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"美國3監獄人員涉向囚犯「洗腦式」播《Baby Shark》遭起訴虐待囚犯體罰等罪<br />\n<br />\n英文兒歌《Baby Shark》自2016年推出以來於社交網絡熱播，深受幼童及家長歡迎。然而在美國俄克拉荷馬州，有3名監獄人員涉嫌向被鎖上手扣的囚犯「洗腦式」播放該歌曲，周一（5日）遭當地地區法院起訴。<br />\n涉案人員包括兩名21歲縣監獄員工，以及他們的一名上司。調查發現3人去年11月和12月，最少5次在監獄內用把囚犯帶到一間未被使用的會見律師房間，迫使鎖上手扣的囚犯面壁罰企，並以電腦播放《Baby Shark》長達兩小時。他們涉及的罪名包括虐待囚犯、對囚犯施體罰及圖謀不軌。兩名員工在內部調查期間已請辭，兩人的上司則已退休。<br />\n<br />\n當地檢察官表示，3人的行為是合謀、故意和錯誤的，以殘酷和不人道的方式對待囚犯，又稱重複播放歌曲，使原本已被鎖上手扣面壁的囚犯增添不必要的情感壓力。法庭文件亦指出，最少兩名涉事囚犯是在凌晨被帶到房間「洗腦式」聽《Baby Shark》受罰，令睡眠受到干擾。<br />\n<br />\n（紐約時報/霍士新聞）<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20201007/s00005/1602062295996/美國3監獄人員涉向囚犯「洗腦式」播《baby-shark》-遭起訴虐待囚犯體罰等罪\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20201007%2Fs00005%2F1602062295996%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B3%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%B6%89%E5%90%91%E5%9B%9A%E7%8A%AF%E3%80%8C%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8D%E6%92%AD%E3%80%8Ababy-shark%E3%80%8B-%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E5%9B%9A%E7%8A%AF%E9%AB%94%E7%BD%B0%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=4358543f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20201007%2Fs00005%2F1602062295996%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B3%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E6%B6%89%E5%90%91%E5%9B%9A%E7%8A%AF%E3%80%8C%E6%B4%97%E8%85%A6%E5%BC%8F%E3%80%8D%E6%92%AD%E3%80%8Ababy-shark%E3%80%8B-%E9%81%AD%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E8%99%90%E5%BE%85%E5%9B%9A%E7%8A%AF%E9%AB%94%E7%BD%B0%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA&h=f8d77c8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20201007/s00005/1602062295996/美國3監獄人員涉向囚犯「洗腦式」播《baby-shark》-遭起訴虐待囚犯體罰等罪</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3def86a73659da35cb90b7901cf8c7298bf24cf5","tid":2233890,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:53:22.000Z","msg":"圖謀不軌"},{"pid":"c7b891633b1ed71153cc1909793b8ea93c28e0c3","tid":2233890,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff281bbe4af691306541965fce735340f1a03662","tid":2233890,"uid":284429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:54:47.000Z","msg":"香港會播起來起來起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09117d5421819665437bc5600dc875327c48c9a3","tid":2233890,"uid":74361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6bPXC5k0M90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6bPXC5k0M90&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=05769d30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6bPXC5k0M90</a>"},{"pid":"f54ad57331b614a684a2f8bca1a1239da2ea2d09","tid":2233890,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"但係香港黑警虐待義士、姦淫擄略、作奸犯科、走私販毒都無後果"},{"pid":"01dcb17b00b40e1c9347c28993bc39c7708fcd2a","tid":2233890,"uid":60393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff281bbe4af691306541965fce735340f1a03662","tid":2233890,"uid":284429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-